mod = op.models.geometry.throat_shape_factor.mason_morrow
self.geo.add_model(propname='throat.shape_factor', model=mod,
    throat_perimeter='throat.perimeter', throat_area='throat.area',
    regen_mode='normal')
a = np.unique(self.geo['throat.shape_factor'])
b = np.array(0.10132118, ndmin=1)
assert np.allclose(a, b)
